#cinemabreakdown #starwars #videoessay 

The most controversial Star Wars film ends with one of its most powerful scenes — Luke Skywalker facing the First Order alone… without ever being there. This video breaks down how The Last Jedi transformed its most hated moment into a cinematic myth.

We’ll explore the symbolism, legacy, and bold narrative choices behind Luke’s final stand — a moment that challenged fans, subverted expectations, and redefined what it means to be a Jedi.
